effects.name: acuity enhancement
effects.body:
Acuity enhancement can be described as an enhancement of the clearness and clarity of vision.
It is most commonly induced under the influence of mild dosages of psychedelic compounds, such as LSD, psilocybin, and mescaline.

effects.name: framerate enhancement
effects.body:
Frame rate enhancement can be described as an effect which increases the detail at which a person can perceive quickly occurring events that appear within their field of view.
It is most commonly induced under the influence of moderate dosages of psychedelic compounds, such as LSD, psilocybin, and mescaline.
